-- OCBC Q2 net profit up 54 pct, beats expectations
-- By Saeed Azhar
-- Mon Aug 04, 2014 07:14PM EDT
-- None



SINGAPORE, Aug 5 (Reuters) - Oversea-Chinese Banking Corp <OCBC.SI>, Singapore's second-biggest lender, posted a 54 percent rise in quarterly profit on Tuesday, beating expectations thanks to brisk loan growth and a strong performance from its insurance unit.

